# Sidebar (L1 Navigation)

## Container
- BG: `bg-[#e7f1f8]`
- Width: `w-[88px]` fixed
- Layout: vertical flex with `gap-8`
- Position: `relative` (contains L2)

## Logo
- Size: 56px square at top

## Nav Items
- Width: `w-[60px]`
- Icon container: `h-8 w-[60px] rounded-[32px]`
- Active: `bg-[#b1e6fb]` (sky blue 100)
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#fafafa]`
- Label: `text-[10px] leading-[12px]`, bold when active
- Icon: `size-6`
- Spacing: `gap-4` between items

## Divider
- Between main and bottom nav
- `bg-[#e0e0e0] h-1 w-8 rounded-[7px]`

---

# L2 Submenu (Settings Panel)

## Trigger
Clicking "Settings" nav item opens the L2 submenu.

## Container
- Position: `absolute left-[88px]` (adjacent to L1)
- Width: `w-[236px]`
- Height: full parent height
- BG: `bg-[#e7f1f8]` (same as L1)
- Border: `border-l border-border`
- Top-right corner: `rounded-tr-[16px]`
- Shadow: `shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)]`
- Padding: `pt-[22px] px-2`
- Z-index: `z-10`

## Category Headers
- Text: `text-[12px] tracking-[0.6px] uppercase font-semibold text-[#101010] leading-[16px]`
- Padding: `px-[12px] py-[16px]`
- Chevron: `size-6 text-[#101010]`, hover: `hover:bg-[#e0e0e0]` (on icon only)
- Rotates 180deg when collapsed

## Menu Items
- Layout: `flex items-center gap-[8px]`
- Padding: `p-[12px]`
- Border radius: `rounded-[12px]`
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#b1e6fb]/50`
- Active: `bg-[#b1e6fb]`
- Icon: `size-6 text-[#101010]`
- Label: `text-[14px] font-medium leading-[20px] text-[#101010]`

## Behavior
- Click outside closes submenu (`useRef` + `useEffect`)
- Clicking other nav items closes submenu
- First category expanded by default
- Smooth transitions: `transition-colors`, `transition-transform`
